# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# Expanded retrieval-eval corpus for Yggdrasil.
# Three module-level lists:
#   CORPUS               : (label, project, mtype, content)
#   CASES                : (query, expected_label, project, klass, split)
#   CROSS_PROJECT_CASES  : (query, expected_label)
#
# Invariants (enforced by the eval harness self-check):
#   - every label in CORPUS is globally unique
#   - every expected_label in CASES / CROSS_PROJECT_CASES exists in CORPUS
#   - in CASES, project == the project of expected_label
#   - within a single project, each memory is a clearly distinct topic
#
# klass values: keyword | identifier | paraphrase | crosslingual
# mtype values: debugging_lesson | decision | convention | fix | command | note | reference | project_status

